trans-unit.source: Specifies a palette when setting a `Palette` property.
trans-unit.target: Especifica uma paleta ao definir um `Palette` propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The ChartColorPalette enumeration represents the palettes to be used for the root <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object and any <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> objects.
trans-unit.target: A enumeração de ChartColorPalette representa as paletas a ser usado para a raiz <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>objeto e qualquer <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>objetos.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If no colors are assigned to data points and their associated series, the default colors will be assigned to the data.
trans-unit.target: Se nenhum cores são atribuídas a pontos de dados e sua série associada, as cores padrão serão atribuídas aos dados.

trans-unit.source: For example: - If <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A> is set to None, then the default palette is set to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A> or BrightPastel.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo: - se <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>está definida como None, a paleta padrão será definido como <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A>ou BrightPastel.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>

trans-unit.source: - If.<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A> is set to None, then the default palette for the chart is used (<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>).
trans-unit.target: -Se. <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A>está definida como None, a paleta padrão para o gráfico será usada (<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>).</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A>
Utiliza a paleta de cores brilhantes.
Utiliza a paleta de cores pastel brilhantes.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes earth tone colors such as green and brown.
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta de cores earth tone como verde e marrom
Utiliza a paleta de cores do estilo do Excel

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes red, orange and yellow colors.
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta de cores vermelho, laranjas e amarelas.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes grayscale colors, that is, shades of black and white.
trans-unit.target: Paleta utiliza em escala de cinza cores, ou seja, tons de preto e branco.
Utiliza a paleta de cores claras.
Utiliza a paleta de cores pastel.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes colors that range from green to blue.
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta de cores que variam de verde para azul
